Package: Sova
Type: Package
Title: A package for Gene types
Version: 1.0.0
Author: Flavia Leotta
Maintainer: Flavia Leotta <flavia.leotta@hotmail.com>
Description: This package provides a set of S4 classes for different gene types (e.g., protein-coding genes, non-coding RNA genes, microRNA genes, ...) inherited from a virtual Gene class.
